# Security — web_app

## XSS & Content
- Escape and sanitize user content; never `dangerouslySetInnerHTML`
- Use CSP headers (nonce/sha256) and disallow inline scripts

## Tokens & Secrets
- No secrets in client bundle; use env only for public keys prefixed `VITE_`
- Store auth tokens in httpOnly cookies; avoid localStorage

## Network
- SameSite and Secure cookies; HTTPS only
- CSRF protection for state-changing requests

## Dependencies
- Pin versions; run vulnerability scans in CI
- Review changelogs before upgrades

## Clickjacking & Mixed Content
- `X-Frame-Options: DENY` (unless explicitly needed)
- Block mixed content; upgrade insecure requests